		<div class="quote"><p>You could argue that this test holds for <em>any</em> relationship—i.e., any ongoing interaction with <em>any</em> other person, corporate entity, whatever: <a href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Axiology">values</a> determine the direction—not to mention the material outcomes—you're working toward. If there's any conflict or divergence there, you're eventually going to feel it.
</p>
</div>
